          </li>
          <li class="leading-normal">
            <a class="text-blue-light text-sm no-underline mt-4 mb-4" href="http://www.slb.com/seed/">
              Schlumberger Excellence in Education Development (SEED)
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="xxs:w-320 xsml:w-375 xsm:w-425 smm:w-480 sm:w-600 md:w-240 border-b">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex">
    <div class="xxs:w-95p md:mx-auto lg:w-240">
      <div class="xxs:vlx p-10 vl">
        <span class="text-base font-bold pb-3">Credits and Administration</span>
